  EffectDiscription_ENG: "[Digivolve] [Mamemon]: Cost 1\n[Digivolve] Lv.4 w/[DM]\_trait:
    Cost 3 \n\nWhen this card would be played, by trashing 1 [Cyborg] or [Ver.2]\_trait
    card from your hand, reduce the play cost by 2.\n[On Play] [When Digivolving]
    By placing 1 Digimon card from your trash face down as this Digimon's bottom
    digivolution card, from 1 of your opponent's Digimon, trash any 1 digivolution
    card for each of this Digimon's face-down digivolution cards. Then, return 1
    of their Digimon with no digivolution cards to the bottom of the deck."
